des: Play with Family for friends and try to score the maximum number of points to prove you're the best. Fun interactive way to engage with your loved ones. This trivia doesn't contain super-easy questions, so don't be fooled that this is like the rest. Only people with Bollywod and Hindi Movies in their veins will do well. But nevertheless, you can try, right?
